feedback: {{ $json.data['If No, write your comments here:'] }}

Your task:
Create a professional, engaging, ready-to-publish LinkedIn post based on the above results and reviewer feedback. 
Use the previous draft as a base. Make improvements only where necessary according to the reviewer feedback. 
The post must:
1. Start with a hook (1-2 lines)
2. Include key insights or highlights (2-3 sentences or bullet points)
